a general partnership. Which means that the investors who fund and particip=
ate in running it are, arguably, general partners. Shareholders of a corpor=
ation are not generally liable for the corporation=E2=80=99s actions, but g=
eneral partners of a partnership generally <em>are</em>. For instance, they=
 might be liable for its unregistered sales of securities.</p>
