<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I remember the days of crypto optimism in 2021=
. One thing that crypto enthusiasts and venture capitalists liked to say wa=
s that crypto was a new way of organizing human economic behavior, that cry=
pto would enable a new =E2=80=9CWeb3=E2=80=9D in which technology was organ=
ized collectively and belonged to its users instead of being owned by big c=
orporations. This could seem pretty cynical, as VC firms often owned big st=
akes in (the tokens of) these web3 projects.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But also it was just a big factual mistake! Cr=
ypto and DAOs and web3 were not a new way of organizing human economic beha=
